## How to Run
1. Clone this repository: git clone <your-repo-link>
2. Open bmi_calculator.ipynb in jupyter Notebook
3. Run all cells from top to bottom shift + Enter
4. Enter details for 3 peopl3 when prompted
5. Check bmi_reports.txt for saved results

